Scandal is an American rock band from the 1980s fronted by Patty Smyth .
The band scored a hit in the United States with the song `` The Warrior '' , which peaked at No. 7 in 1984 .
Other minor hits were `` Goodbye to You '' -LRB- 1982 - No. 65 US -RRB- , `` Love 's Got A Line On You '' -LRB- 1983 - No. 59 US -RRB- , `` Hands Tied '' -LRB- 1984 - No. 41 US -RRB- , and `` Beat of A Heart '' -LRB- 1985 - No. 41 US -RRB- .